1
00:00:02,730 --> 00:00:05,960
那个女孩一定在跟我使眼色 她才没有
-She totally winked at me! -She did not wink at you.

2
00:00:06,230 --> 00:00:08,700
你总是以为 别人在跟你使眼色
You always think somebody's winking at you.

3
00:00:22,450 --> 00:00:24,650
本集播出： “莉亚公主的幻想”
The One With the Princess Leia Fantasy

4
00:01:10,430 --> 00:01:13,030
我会认为是 范莫里森（爱尔兰民谣歌手）的“土波罗蜜”
I say "Tupelo Honey" by Van Morrison.

5
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:14,500
不会吧！
No way!

6
00:01:14,770 --> 00:01:17,600
我会认为 最浪漫的曲子是“往日情怀”
The most romantic song ever was "The Way We Were."

7
00:01:17,810 --> 00:01:22,610
我觉得是艾尔顿约翰为连续剧《妙管家》里的家伙写的歌
I think the one that Elton John wrote for that guy on Who's the Boss?

8
00:01:25,050 --> 00:01:26,170
那是什么歌？
What song was that?

9
00:01:26,420 --> 00:01:30,280
“抱紧我，年轻的汤尼丹佐”（应该是“抱紧我，小舞者”）
Hold me close Young Tony Danza

10
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,920
莫妮卡 莫妮卡
-Hi,Monica. -Hi,Mon.

11
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,490
天啊
Oh,my God!

12
00:01:41,830 --> 00:01:43,630
她到底有没有睡觉？
Has she slept at all?

13
00:01:43,870 --> 00:01:45,600
没有 已经连续三个晚上了
It's been three nights in a row.

14
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:47,770
从昨天起，她终于不哭了
She finally stopped crying yesterday.

15
00:01:47,970 --> 00:01:51,770
但是她又在阳台发现 理查抽过的雪茄
But then she found one of Richard's cigar butts on the terrace....

16
00:01:52,010 --> 00:01:55,540
好吧，这说明了为何我在 清晨两点接到一通电话
Okay,that explains it. I got a call at 2 in the morning...

17
00:01:55,810 --> 00:01:58,210
而我只能听到一些吱吱的声音
...and all I could hear was this squeaky sound.

18
00:01:58,450 --> 00:02:00,810
我就想“一定是老鼠或负鼠”
So I thought,"It's a mouse or a possum."

19
00:02:02,690 --> 00:02:04,710
然后我就想，好吧…
Then I realized,like,okay...

20
00:02:04,990 --> 00:02:09,890
老鼠或负鼠怎么会 有钱打电话呢？
...where would a mouse or a possum get the money to make the phone call?

21
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:14,520
早安 早啊
-Morning. -Morning.

22
00:02:15,570 --> 00:02:17,060
你做了松饼啊？
You made pancakes?

23
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:21,000
是啊，你还以为我真的会做呢
Yeah,like there's any way I could ever do that.

24
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:24,630
莫妮卡和瑞秋有糖浆
Monica and Rachel had syrup

25
00:02:25,540 --> 00:02:28,070
我可以让我的男人开心了
Now I can get my man to cheer up

26
00:02:30,710 --> 00:02:31,910
早安，乔伊
Good morning,Joey.

27
00:02:32,180 --> 00:02:33,180
早安
Good morning.

28
00:02:33,380 --> 00:02:36,540
有人穿着坏脾气的裤子哦
Someone's wearing grumpy pants.

29
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:39,850
那一定说的是你，我穿着傲慢无礼的裤子
lt's gotta be you, man.l'm wearing smarty-pants.

30
00:02:40,050 --> 00:02:42,890
好了，开始了，一，二
Okay, here we go: One, two...

31
00:02:43,090 --> 00:02:48,290
侥幸给你第三个
...and here's my chance to give you a third one.

32
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:51,800
-乔伊？-不，我只喝果汁就行了
-Joey? -No, no. l'll just have juice.

33
00:02:53,070 --> 00:02:56,870
你干脆别去上班 跟我在一起就好了
Why don't you stay home from work and just hang out with me?

34
00:02:57,180 --> 00:02:58,070
是啊，但愿如此
Oh,I wish.

35
00:02:58,310 --> 00:03:02,080
你有报告要做 而我得去见律师
You have that report to finish,and I've got to see my lawyer.

36
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:04,970
我真不敢相信 我竟跟要离婚的女生约会
I can't believe I date a girl who's getting divorced.

37
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:07,010
我真像个大人
I'm such a grownup.

38
00:03:07,250 --> 00:03:10,650
乔伊，嘿，回你的房间
Joey! Hey!Go to your room!

39
00:03:11,150 --> 00:03:14,220
钱德，嘿，去你的
Chandler! Hey!Up yours!

40
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,650
我要走了…
I gotta go,I gotta go.

41
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,220
给我个吻才能走
Not without a kiss.

42
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:20,490
或者我就不亲你 这样你就会留下来
Maybe I won't kiss you so you'll stay.

43
00:03:20,730 --> 00:03:22,130
快亲她…
Kiss her. Kiss her!

44
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:27,300
晚点见，甜心 再见，乔伊
I'll see you later,sweetie. Bye,Joey.

45
00:03:27,510 --> 00:03:29,560
再见，珍妮丝
Bye-bye,Janice.

46
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:33,270
你什么时候要甩掉她？
When are you dumping her?

47
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,500
不会
Nope.

48
00:03:34,780 --> 00:03:36,250
这次不会了
Not this time.

49
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:38,450
拜托，别整我了
Come on,quit yanking me.

50
00:03:41,990 --> 00:03:43,580
我没有整你
I'm not yanking you.

51
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:47,180
这个是珍妮丝 对，我知道
-This is Janice. -Yeah,I know.

52
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,920
她让我很愉快
She makes me happy.

53
00:03:52,460 --> 00:03:55,860
好，你看着我的眼睛 告诉我，不可以眨眼睛
You look me in the eye and tell me,without blinking...

54
00:03:56,130 --> 00:03:58,830
说你不会跟她分手 别眨眼睛
...that you're not breaking up with her. No blinking.

55
00:04:01,870 --> 00:04:03,500
我不会跟她分手！
I'm not breaking up with her!

56
00:04:12,180 --> 00:04:14,710
天啊，你看我在排水管里 发现什么？
God,look what I found in the drain!

57
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:16,210
什么？
What?

58
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:19,190
这些是理查的头发！
It's some of Richard's hair!

59
00:04:19,990 --> 00:04:21,390
我该拿这些怎么办？
What do I do with this?

60
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:24,560
第一件事就是 把它从我身边拿开
Getting it away from me would be job one.

61
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:28,820
奇怪，但我并不想把它丢掉
It's weird,but I don't want to throw this away.

62
00:04:29,070 --> 00:04:30,970
这些是我仅有的 属于他的东西
This is all I have left of him.

63
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,730
恶心的…
Gross...

64
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:34,700
排水管的头发
...drain hair.

65
00:04:41,050 --> 00:04:46,140
真好玩，好像有一个小人 在你的麦片里淹死了
Cool! It looks like a tiny little person drowning in your cereal.

66
00:04:48,890 --> 00:04:51,880
我是怎么了？ 你需要一些睡眠
-What is wrong with me? -You need to get some sleep.

67
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:54,150
我需要的是理查
I need to get some Richard.

68
00:04:57,060 --> 00:04:59,190
你跟他分手是有原因的
You broke up with him for a reason.

69
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:03,390
我知道… 我只是不想再这么想他
I know. I know. I'm just so tired of missing him.

70
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:06,660
不愿再去想，他为何不打来？ 他为何都没打来？
Tired of wondering why he hasn't called. Why hasn't he?

71
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:08,930
可能因为你叫他别再打来？
Maybe because you told him not to?

72
00:05:09,770 --> 00:05:11,870
你到底是什么？ 记忆女王吗？
What are you,the Memory Woman?

73
00:05:14,050 --> 00:05:16,040
他们不会分手！ 我是说钱德和珍妮丝
They're not breaking up! Chandler and Janice?

74
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:18,710
他们不会分手！ 他的眼睛连眨一下都没有
They're not breaking up! He didn't blink!

75
00:05:20,180 --> 00:05:22,710
我一点也不惊讶 你看过他们在一起的样子吗？
I'm not surprised. Have you seen them together?

76
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,080
他们真的好可爱
They're really cute.

77
00:05:24,290 --> 00:05:26,350
“可爱？”那可是珍妮丝！
"Cute"? This is Janice!

78
00:05:27,460 --> 00:05:28,720
你记得珍妮丝吗？
You remember Janice?

79
00:05:28,930 --> 00:05:31,450
我记得啊，她很惹人厌 但是你知道吗？
Yes,I remember. She's annoying. But you know what?

80
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:34,260
她现在是他的女朋友 那我们能怎么办？
She's his girlfriend now. I mean,what can we do?

81
00:05:34,570 --> 00:05:38,130
这就对了，我就是要这种精神 “我们能怎么办？”
There you go! That's the spirit I'm looking for! "What can we do?"

82
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:42,710
好，谁先来？罗斯？
All right,who's first,huh? Ross?

83
00:05:42,940 --> 00:05:45,470
钱德是我们的朋友 而珍妮丝能让他快乐
Chandler's our friend,and Janice makes him happy.

84
00:05:45,780 --> 00:05:48,440
所以我们就成熟点，接受她
So I say we be adult about it and accept her.

85
00:05:48,710 --> 00:05:50,540
这个先归类在B计划
We'll call that Plan B.

86
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:55,210
拜托，我们需要些妙计
Come on, people!We need some inspiration.

87
00:05:55,420 --> 00:05:57,750
好吧，你需要计划？这样
Okay, all right.You want a plan? Here we go:

88
00:05:57,950 --> 00:06:02,860
那么，罗斯，你爬进排气管，不要触动警报，好吗
So, Ross, you go in through the air duct and disable the alarm, okay?

89
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:05,360
剩下的交给我们，放下绳子就行了
Then the rest of us will rappel down ropes.

90
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:09,890
我们要在十分钟之内进去出来，然后消失在夜色中，好吗？
We're in and out in 10 minutes and disappear into the night. Huh?

91
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:32,680
甜心…
Honey...

92
00:06:33,090 --> 00:06:34,450
我在想啊…
... I was wondering...

93
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:38,520
你那套海军制服还在吗？
...do you still have that Navy uniform?

94
00:06:40,890 --> 00:06:44,060
不，我拿去戏服店还了
No,I had to return it to the costume place.

95
00:06:44,430 --> 00:06:47,090
我还有一套 高中乐团的旧制服
I think I have an old band uniform from high school.

96
00:06:48,030 --> 00:06:50,930
你记得高中时不能做爱吧？ 是啊
You remember not having sex in high school,right?

97
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:58,440
甜心，那么你呢…
Well,honey,what about you?

98
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:04,870
你有任何有趣的幻想吗？
Do you have any fun,you know,fantasy-type things?

99
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:11,080
别这样，你一定有
Come on. You gotta have one.

100
00:07:12,290 --> 00:07:13,120
没有
Nope.

101
00:07:14,260 --> 00:07:15,780
罗斯，你知道吗？
You know what?

102
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:18,960
如果你跟我说 或许我会帮你实现
If you tell me,I might do it.

103
00:07:31,310 --> 00:07:34,750
你有没有看过《星球大战》的《绝地大反攻》？
Did you ever see Return of the Jedi?

104
00:07:44,190 --> 00:07:46,920
你记不记得那场戏…
Do you remember the scene...

105
00:07:48,490 --> 00:07:50,090
当赫特族的贾霸出现时？
...with Jabba the Hutt?

106
00:07:52,930 --> 00:07:57,130
他真是个胖胖的虫子怪物
He was this really fat worm guy.

107
00:07:57,610 --> 00:08:00,270
哇哦，男人和女人的兴趣果然不一样
Wow. Men and women really are different.

108
00:08:01,410 --> 00:08:02,400
不，不，不
No. No. No.

109
00:08:02,610 --> 00:08:05,440
贾霸带着他的囚犯…
Well,Jabba had as his prisoner...

110
00:08:06,710 --> 00:08:08,080
莉亚公主
... Princess Leia.

111
00:08:12,050 --> 00:08:15,040
莉亚公主穿着…
Princess Leia was wearing...

112
00:08:15,790 --> 00:08:17,760
金色的比基尼
...this gold bikini thing.

113
00:08:20,790 --> 00:08:22,190
那样子很好看
It was pretty cool.

114
00:08:25,170 --> 00:08:29,160
所以你是说你想让我…
So are you saying that you would like me...

115
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:33,800
打扮成莉亚公主，穿着金色的比基尼？
...to dress up like Princess Leia in a gold bikini?

116
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:35,840
好
Okay

117
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:41,950
莉亚公主穿金色比基尼？ 我们这年纪的男人都很喜欢
Princess Leia and the gold bikini? Every guy our age loved that.

118
00:08:43,830 --> 00:08:44,850
真的吗？
Really?

119
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:49,660
很重要的！ 那个时刻，她不再是个公主
It's huge! That's the moment when she stopped being a princess...

120
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:52,660
她变成了…一个女人
...and she became,like,you know,a woman.

121
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:57,370
你曾扮过莉亚公主吗？
Did you ever do the Leia thing?

122
00:09:03,110 --> 00:09:05,550
真的吗？有那么棒啊？
Really? That great,huh?

123
00:09:06,050 --> 00:09:10,490
不，只是我买了新的传呼机 我把它调成“震动”
No,it's just that I got this new pager,and I have it on "vibrate."

124
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:15,280
再见
See you.

125
00:09:17,190 --> 00:09:18,130
你们好啊
Hi,you guys!

126
00:09:18,330 --> 00:09:21,390
你看我在四川龙餐厅外 找到谁了？
Look who I found standing outside the Szechuan Dragon...

127
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:23,900
她盯着停车收费表看
...staring at a parking meter.

128
00:09:28,570 --> 00:09:31,730
你怎么没去上班？ 他们把我送回家了
-Why aren't you at work? -Oh,they sent me home.

129
00:09:32,010 --> 00:09:33,200
为什么？
Why?

130
00:09:33,710 --> 00:09:36,410
因为我并不是在四川龙餐厅上班
Because I don't work at the Szechuan Dragon.

131
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:38,810
你真的需要睡一下
You really need to get some sleep.

132
00:09:39,050 --> 00:09:40,350
我知道
I know I do.

133
00:09:42,050 --> 00:09:44,080
你猜怎么着？ 有人要出版我的论文
Guess what? They published my paper.

134
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,000
-真的吗？-是的
-Really?-Yes

135
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:52,010
藻类化石的碳定年法误差统计：历史还是神秘？
Statistical Deviations in the Carbon Dating of Fossilized Algae:History or Mystery?

136
00:09:54,090 --> 00:09:55,720
瑞秋，你看！
Rach,look!

137
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:05,240
我那强壮的罗斯天行者 何时会来拯救我？
Where is my strong Ross Skywalker to come rescue me?

138
00:10:10,610 --> 00:10:11,410
他来了！
There he is!

139
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:17,980
-幸运！-的！
-Wheel! -Of!

140
00:10:18,180 --> 00:10:19,340
轮盘！
Fortune!

141
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,350
这个家伙好笨
This guy's so stupid.

142
00:10:22,620 --> 00:10:27,110
是“拉什莫尔伯爵” （应该是拉什莫尔山，刻有美国四位总统头像）
It's Count Rushmore!

143
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,330
你真的该去参加这个节目
You should really go on this show.

144
00:10:32,130 --> 00:10:35,860
我有三张今晚巡游者队的票 你觉得如何？
I got three tickets to the Rangers tonight. What do you say?

145
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:37,970
我一定去！
I say I am there!

146
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,140
太棒了！
Cool!

147
00:10:39,470 --> 00:10:40,960
罗斯也会去吗？
Is Ross going too?

148
00:10:41,210 --> 00:10:42,440
不，是珍妮丝
No. Janice.

149
00:10:42,810 --> 00:10:43,800
珍妮丝？
Janice?

150
00:10:45,950 --> 00:10:49,180
因为我会替罗斯难过 你知道吗？
Because I just feel bad for Ross,you know?

151
00:10:49,380 --> 00:10:53,980
我们总是一起去的 我们是曲棍球三兄弟啊
We always go together. We're like The Three Hockey-teers,you know?

152
00:10:54,550 --> 00:10:58,990
我可能误会你了 但你是否不喜欢珍妮丝？
I may be way out on a limb here,but do you have a problem with Janice?

153
00:10:59,190 --> 00:11:00,160
没有
No!

154
00:11:01,530 --> 00:11:02,690
对啦…
Yes....

155
00:11:03,460 --> 00:11:05,860
天啊，我该怎么说？
Oh,God,how do I say this?

156
00:11:09,470 --> 00:11:11,960
你知道希腊餐厅里 那个头发很蓬的女孩子？
You know that girl from the restaurant with the hair?

157
00:11:12,170 --> 00:11:14,970
那个我很讨厌的女孩子？ 她快把我逼疯了
That girl that I hate? She drives me crazy.

158
00:11:17,540 --> 00:11:21,570
听着，我不讨厌珍妮丝 只是她令人难以忍受
Look,I don't hate Janice. She's just a lot to take,you know?

159
00:11:24,250 --> 00:11:25,550
你说出来了吧
Well,there you go.

160
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:28,550
别那样看着我
Don't look at me like that.

161
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:31,090
以前她也快把你逼疯了 记得吗？
She drove you nuts before,remember?

162
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:34,490
但是我现在为她疯狂 这次可能是真的
I'm crazy about her now. This could be the real thing.

163
00:11:34,730 --> 00:11:36,700
我是说“真的”
Capital R,capital T!

164
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:41,530
别担心，我说的字母是对的
Don't worry,those are the right letters.

165
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:45,500
你到底要我说什么？
Look,what do you want me to say?

166
00:11:46,340 --> 00:11:48,760
我要你说你喜欢她！ 我不能
I want you to say that you like her! I can't

167
00:11:48,970 --> 00:11:51,270
-喜欢她！-不！
-Like her!-No.

168
00:11:51,470 --> 00:11:53,100
你甚至不想尝试？
