你觉得他是否等你走后 才一个人开始哭？
Do you think he was waiting till after you left,so he could cry?

338
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,470
或许吧
Maybe.

339
00:22:59,510 --> 00:23:00,840
我想也是
I think so.

340
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:04,370
宝贝，感情这回事很难说 就像我跟你妈
Honey,relationships are hard. Like with your mom and me.

341
00:23:04,580 --> 00:23:08,350
大学毕业后 我们曾分手一阵子
You know,after we graduated from college,we broke up for a while.

342
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:11,050
她父亲，就是你祖父，似乎…
It seems her father,your grandfather...

343
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:13,910
希望你妈跟他一样 到欧洲四处旅行…
...wanted her to travel around Europe like he did.

344
00:23:14,190 --> 00:23:16,850
当然，他是为了山姆大叔（美国政府）…
Of course,he got to do it on Uncle Sam's nickel...

345
00:23:17,090 --> 00:23:21,430
因为当时他也在猛轰德国的军用运输列车
... because he was also strafing German troop trains at the time.

346
00:23:21,660 --> 00:23:22,430
然而…
However....

347
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:05,960
好吧，开始啰
Okay,here we go.

348
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:09,410
我是贾霸的囚犯，而你…
I am Jabba's prisoner. And you...

349
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:12,440
你脸上的表情好怪
... have a really weird look on your face.

350
00:24:12,950 --> 00:24:14,280
怎么了，甜心？ 有什么问题？
What? Honey,what is it?

351
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:15,970
我的头发不对吗？
Did I get the hair wrong?

352
00:24:16,280 --> 00:24:20,010
还是别的问题？ 跟你想像的不同，还是…？
Or what? Did you just picture it differently? What?

353
00:24:20,290 --> 00:24:22,480
不是你的问题，是…
It's not you. It's....

354
00:24:27,430 --> 00:24:31,520
怎么了？拜托，甜心 你快把我吓坏了
What is it? Come on,sweetie. You're,like,freaking me out here.

355
00:24:34,100 --> 00:24:36,830
我恨钱德 那个混蛋毁了我的人生！
I hate Chandler. The bastard ruined my life!


